Package gw.api.web.invoice

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InvoiceItemViewFormatter
    Formatter for displaying things like the Status of an InvoiceItem and/or SnapshotInvoiceItem
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgencyBillInvoiceItemView
    Class used to display a single invoice item on an Agency Bill statement
    AgencyBillStatementView  
    AgencyDistExceptionView
    View class that represents a list of exception items.
    AnchorDateView
    A View for editing and displaying the anchor dates of invoice streams.
    ChargeOwnerWithInvoiceItemsView
    Class used to display a single policy period (or other charge owner) and its invoice items on an Agency Bill Statement.
    ExceptionItemView
    View class that displays information about one exception item from an Agency Payment
    InvoiceItems  
    InvoiceStreamView
    A View for editing and displaying Invoice Streams.
    InvoiceUtil  
    InvoicingOverrider
    This class manages setting the invoicing overrides fields on an invoicing overridable It collects the information needed to set the overrides on an InvoicingOverridable The invoicingOverridable calls InvoicingOverridable.updateWith(InvoicingOverrider) and the overrides defined by this class are set on the overridable and the invoice items are moved to the correct payer and stream, if needed.
    ProducerWithExceptionsView
    POJO encapsulating a Producer and metadata about its ExceptionItems.
